snippet.title: マカブルの残党: Remnants of the Macabre | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Step into a chilling world set in 1980s Japan, inspired by the haunting tales of Junji Ito. You are a schoolgirl on your way home, navigating an urban street filled with sinister and unsettling details. Each step you take, each choice you make, can lead you closer to safety or deeper into the unknown.
